'''Shelter Base''' was a [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Galactic Republic]] command center set up on [[Jabiim/Legends|Jabiim]] during the [[Battle of Jabiim]] in the [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]]. It was destroyed in an [[Battle of Shelter Base|attack]] by [[Alto Stratus]] and his [[Nimbus commando]]s.

